response.overview: Joker: Folie à Deux (2024) is the continuation of Arthur Fleck’s story following his turbulent climb to the role of Joker. Now imprisoned in Arkham Asylum, he encounters Dr. Harleen Quinzel, a psychiatrist captivated by his personality. As she dives deeper into his psyche, Quinzel is dragged into Arthur’s world.
response.tagline: The tagline for "Joker: Folie à Deux" is "The world is a stage."
response.title: Joker: Folie à Deux 2024
